# BF Agent - Django Multi-Agent Development Platform

## 🚨 ABSOLUTE PRIORITY RULE #1: FIX TOOLS FIRST, NOT GENERATED CODE

### THE GOLDEN RULE
**NEVER fix generated code manually. ALWAYS fix the generator first.**

### MANDATORY WORKFLOW
1. Error in generated file? → STOP!
2. Don't fix the file
3. Find the generator that created it
4. Fix the generator
5. Regenerate
6. Test

### WHY?
- One fix → All future generations fixed
- Sustainable solution
- No recurring bugs
- Framework improves continuously

### DETECTION TRIGGERS
- File contains "AUTO-GENERATED" comment → Fix generator!
- File created by [consistency_framework.py](cci:7://file:///C:/Users/achim/github/bfagent/scripts/consistency_framework.py:0:0-0:0) → Fix generator!
- Same error repeats → Fix source tool!
- Import errors in views/forms/templates → Fix ViewGenerator/FormGenerator/TemplateGenerator!

